27:05.824 --> 27:08.126 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CRISTI IFRIMESCU, Father of
Raluca (through
translator): What counts is for
the child

27:08.160 --> 27:12.631 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
