allowed to
talk to you because when Red
Riding Hood talked

28:04.583 --> 28:17.095 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
to the wolf, he ate her."

28:17.129 --> 28:24.870 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NARRATOR: Elementary school is
free in Romania,
but even in first grade, Cristi
and Mirela

28:24.903 --> 28:27.172 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
find that the little extras add
up.

28:27.205 --> 28:33.478 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIRELA IFRIMESCU (through
translator): By
the end of the month, we have no
money left.

28:33.512 --> 28:40.552 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We wonder how the others who
make less money
than us can manage. How do they
survive?

28:40.586 --> 28:46.858 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NARRATOR: Cristi works as a
technician at
a printing press, and Mirela is
an accountant.

28:46.892 --> 28:51.997 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CRISTI IFRIMESCU (through
translator): It's
a great thing that we both have
a job. It

28:52.030 --> 29:02.741 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
matters a lot. We hope, since we
consider
ourselves still young, that
things will change.

29:02.774 --> 29:04.977 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And we hope for a better life.

29:05.010 --> 29:12.618 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RALUCA (through translator): On
manga anime,
I have 2,145 posts. I also
moderate some Web

29:12.651 --> 29:18.390 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
sites, and I'm the administrator
of others,
and that practically takes up
all my time.

29:18.423 --> 29:27.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CRISTI IFRIMESCU (through
translator): She's
ambitious. And she wants to do
something with

29:27.866 --> 29:32.638 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
her life. We didn't think of
that when we
were kids, because you could
only reach a

29:32.671 --> 29:37.109 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
certain level, and then you had
to stop.

29:37.142 --> 29:46.585 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It wasn't important if you were
smart or not.
It was important who you knew,
if you knew

29:46.618 --> 29:50.055 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
someone who had an important
position in the
Communist Party.

29:50.088 --> 29:56.161 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIRELA IFRIMESCU (through
translator): Now,
you have to be very good to
succeed.

29:56.194 --> 30:02.134 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NARRATOR: Raluca's middle school
is a pressure
cooker, with intense competition
for high

30:02.167 --> 30:03.902 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
marks.

30:03.935 --> 30:07.406 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator):
Calculate the
median line for a trapezoid with
a base of

30:07.439 --> 30:09.441 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
10.

30:09.474 --> 30:11.877 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RALUCA IFRIMESCU (through
translator): I felt
from the first day that there
was a huge difference

30:11.910 --> 30:21.820 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
between them and me, but I
caught up, and
now I'm one of the good
students. I want to

30:21.853 --> 30:25.691 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
be one of the best and have only
10s.

30:25.724 --> 30:31.196 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NARRATOR: It's the night before
a big exam,
and Raluca is having a meltdown.

30:31.229 --> 30:35.434 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RALUCA IFRIMESCU (through
translator): Based
on this mark, I could end up in
a good high

30:35.467 --> 30:40.238 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
school or a bad one. My future
depends on
it.

30:40.272 --> 30:45.544 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NARRATOR: Only those who test at
the very
top will be admitted to the most
competitive

30:45.577 --> 30:46.878 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
high schools.

30:46.912 --> 30:51.249 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CRISTI IFRIMESCU (through
translator): Please,
try to relax.

30:51.283 --> 31:02.160 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RALUCA IFRIMESCU (through
translator): I hope
the test will be easy and I hope
I won't panic,

31:02.194 --> 31:15.140 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
because I tend to panic whether
I know the
answers or not. God gives me
confidence.

31:15.173 --> 31:23.682 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NARRATOR: Raluca did manage to
test into a
good high school. And five years
later, everyone's

31:23.715 --> 31:25.650 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
hard work has paid off.

31:25.684 --> 31:30.255 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RALUCA IFRIMESCU (through
translator): This
is the building where I spent my
four years

31:30.288 --> 31:35.894 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of high school. They were the
most important
years of my life, because I have
learned so

31:35.927 --> 31:37.796 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
much.

31:37.829 --> 31:44.169 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NARRATOR: She graduated from
Bucharest's Economics
High School with a near-perfect
score and

31:44.202 --> 31:45.971 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
was named valedictorian.

31:46.004 --> 31:48.039 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RALUCA IFRIMESCU (through
translator): My
guidance counselor had told me I
would graduate

31:48.073 --> 31:53.845 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
first in the class. My average
grade was 9.9
out of 10. So she told me to
expect something

31:53.879 --> 32:00.318 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
big. It was a beautiful moment,
because I
hadn't really expected it. Was
that really

32:00.352 --> 32:05.090 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
me? I was so emotional. I'm
surprised I didn't
trip over something.

32:05.123 --> 32:16.401 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Memories. I love these guys. I
will always
remember each person and what
they were like.

32:16.434 --> 32:23.041 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I will miss them, yes.

32:23.074 --> 32:27.846 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NARRATOR: Raluca will be leaving
Romania -- an
international business degree at
the University

32:27.879 --> 32:35.453 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
of Warwick in the U.K.,
something her parents
could never have done. Living
under communism,

32:35.487 --> 32:37.322 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
