the country.

32:37.355 --> 32:41.693 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CRISTI IFRIMESCU (through
translator): I hope
she will become somebody
important as quickly

32:41.726 --> 32:50.936 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
