dreams will come
true. We live vicariously
through her dreams.

32:50.969 --> 32:58.343 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NARRATOR: Raluca's chances for
success may
be better abroad. Despite
progress, Romania

32:58.376 --> 33:03.181 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
is still one of the poorest
countries in the
E.U., and one in four
20-somethings are out

33:03.215 --> 33:08.787 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of a job. So, Cristi and Mirela
are preparing
to let go of their only child.

33:08.820 --> 33:12.257 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CRISTI IFRIMESCU (through
translator): Can
we buy an apartment on campus
while you're

33:12.290 --> 33:13.158 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in college?

33:13.191 --> 33:14.459 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

33:14.492 --> 33:17.662 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RALUCA IFRIMESCU (through
translator): No,
I don't think so.

33:17.696 --> 33:26.304 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I will probably be happy on the
first month,
because I will be like, oh, I am
free now.

33:26.338 --> 33:32.244 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I can do anything I want. And my
mother will
not come at 11:00 or 12:00 and
say, turn off

33:32.277 --> 33:34.145 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the computer. You are making so
much noise.

33:34.179 --> 33:35.981 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

33:36.014 --> 33:40.018 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RALUCA IFRIMESCU But after --
and after the
first month, I will miss them
and probably

33:40.051 --> 33:47.792 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I will cry a lot. But I know
that I'm going
to have fun and those years will
be one of

33:47.826 --> 33:51.396 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the amazing things that will
happen to me
ever.

33:51.429 --> 33:53.698 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: What a story.

